@startuml
[*] --> Idle
Idle --> Ready : everything is fine during startup
Ready --> Resetting : user presses reset button
Resetting --> Ready : system resets
Ready --> Activating : user activates system
Activating --> Monitoring : system starts monitoring
Monitoring --> Alarm : sensor triggered
Alarm --> Normal : false alarm or time ends
Normal --> Ready : user enters password
@enduml
